Package: ndr
Title: Named-Dimension Arrays with Coordinate-Based Indexing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Sumner", , "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Variable, DataArray, and Dataset classes for
    N-dimensional arrays with named dimensions and coordinate-based
    indexing. Arithmetic operations broadcast by dimension name, not
    position. Designed as a minimal foundation for lazy, multi-file
    scientific data access â€” the core data structures without any file
    backends.
